01:41:27,554 --> 01:41:30,182
Do you believe in me now?

1211
01:41:31,291 --> 01:41:32,690
MICHAEL:
Yes.

1212
01:41:34,027 --> 01:41:35,995
Yes. I believe in you.

1213
01:41:38,999 --> 01:41:41,092
I believe in the devil.

1214
01:42:04,892 --> 01:42:06,120
<i>I believe in you...</i>

1215
01:42:08,095 --> 01:42:09,722
...so I believe in God.

1216
01:42:12,366 --> 01:42:15,358
I accept him in this moment.
I accept God.

1217
01:42:16,236 --> 01:42:19,569
I believe in God the Father,
the maker of heaven and earth...

1218
01:42:19,740 --> 01:42:22,265
...of all that is seen and unseen.

1219
01:42:22,442 --> 01:42:24,342
I believe.

1220
01:42:24,511 --> 01:42:27,844
I exorcise you, most unclean spirit.

1221
01:42:28,015 --> 01:42:30,540
Warp of vices, creator of agony.

1222
01:42:30,717 --> 01:42:33,413
In the name of Jesus Christ,
leave this man.

1223
01:42:33,587 --> 01:42:36,112
In the name of the Virgin Mary,
leave now.

1224
01:42:36,323 --> 01:42:37,449
I command you.

1225
01:42:37,891 --> 01:42:39,381
I, who believe.

1226
01:42:39,560 --> 01:42:41,619
In the name of our Lord, Jesus Christ...

1227
01:42:41,795 --> 01:42:44,593
...be uprooted and expelled
from this creature of God.

1228
01:42:44,765 --> 01:42:47,700
He who commands you is he
who ordered you to be thrown down...

1229
01:42:47,868 --> 01:42:50,393
...from the highest heaven
into the depths of hell.

1230
01:42:50,571 --> 01:42:53,540
Hear therefore and fear,
Satan, enemy of faith.

1231
01:42:53,707 --> 01:42:57,575
Fear him who was crucified as man
and who rose from death!

1232
01:42:59,746 --> 01:43:01,475
I will never leave you, Michael.

1233
01:43:05,018 --> 01:43:07,612
I will never leave you.

1234
01:43:10,457 --> 01:43:12,687
[GROWLING AND THUDDING]

1235
01:43:20,267 --> 01:43:21,757
Speak your name.

1236
01:43:24,071 --> 01:43:27,905
In the name of Jesus Christ,
I command you, speak your name.

1237
01:43:32,112 --> 01:43:36,014
In the name of the Holy Spirit,
I command you. Give me your name!

1238
01:43:37,918 --> 01:43:40,785
It is God who commands you!
Your name!

1239
01:43:41,154 --> 01:43:42,485
Your name!

1240
01:43:42,656 --> 01:43:43,953
Give me your name!

1241
01:43:45,292 --> 01:43:47,988
Ba'al!

1242
01:43:49,796 --> 01:43:52,492
Ba'al!

1243
01:43:54,368 --> 01:43:57,895
Ba'al!

1244
01:43:59,506 --> 01:44:05,536
Ba'al!

1245
01:44:16,990 --> 01:44:19,652
I know you, Ba'al.

1246
01:44:19,826 --> 01:44:23,819
And I command you, retire therefore.

1247
01:44:24,631 --> 01:44:26,929
Depart from this place. Leave!

1248
01:44:27,434 --> 01:44:29,026
Surrender now.

1249
01:44:29,202 --> 01:44:33,571
In the name of the Father, and
of the Son and of the Holy Spirit...

1250
01:44:33,740 --> 01:44:35,867
...forever and ever.

1251
01:45:17,651 --> 01:45:21,451
[BELL TOLLING]

1252
01:46:05,899 --> 01:46:08,299
It's good as new, huh?

1253
01:46:08,535 --> 01:46:10,025
Yeah.

1254
01:46:10,937 --> 01:46:13,269
Well, she wasn't a bad little bike.

1255
01:46:13,440 --> 01:46:15,340
You know, back in her golden days...

1256
01:46:15,509 --> 01:46:17,670
...she brought me out here
all those years ago.

1257
01:46:18,478 --> 01:46:20,036
<i>Anyway...</i>

1258
01:46:20,280 --> 01:46:22,407
So you're off. You're leaving.

1259
01:46:22,582 --> 01:46:24,106
MICHAEL:
Yeah, that's right.

1260
01:46:24,284 --> 01:46:28,118
Well, I hope you find your place
in the world one of these fine days.

1261
01:46:28,688 --> 01:46:30,212
- I hope so.
- Now, when you do...

1262
01:46:30,390 --> 01:46:33,188
...don't forget to say a few prayers
for an old sinner.

1263
01:46:33,827 --> 01:46:37,388
Throw a couple of Hail Marys this way
if that's not too much trouble.

1264
01:46:37,564 --> 01:46:38,588
That a deal?

1265
01:46:38,999 --> 01:46:41,763
- It's a deal.
- Good.

1266
01:46:44,171 --> 01:46:46,071
You know, the first day
you showed up...

1267
01:46:46,239 --> 01:46:49,902
...I thought you were so full of it, I was
tempted to kick you into the street.

1268
01:46:50,077 --> 01:46:53,911
But I didn't because I saw
quite a bit of myself in you.

1269
01:46:55,148 --> 01:46:56,979
Scary, isn't it?

1270
01:46:57,984 --> 01:47:01,545
- Yeah, it sure is.
- Yeah.

1271
01:47:01,955 --> 01:47:06,187
All right, that's it. Thanks for everything.
Safe journey. And one other thing.

1272
01:47:06,359 --> 01:47:09,328
Faith becomes you. Stay with it.

1273
01:47:09,496 --> 01:47:13,865
Keep fighting the good fight
with all thy might.

1274
01:47:15,402 --> 01:47:17,131
Cool.

1275
01:47:18,605 --> 01:47:20,129
Get out of here.

1276
01:47:25,479 --> 01:47:27,447
Goodbye, Father.

1277
01:49:03,977 --> 01:49:05,842
[KNOCKING]

1278
01:49:11,518 --> 01:49:14,419
WOMAN:
Bless me, Father, for I have sinned.

1279
01:49:14,588 --> 01:49:18,149
It has been six weeks
since my last confession.

1280
01:49:18,625 --> 01:49:20,957
MICHAEL:
And what are your sins?

1281
01:49:22,495 --> 01:49:29,367
Father Michael Kovak is one of 14 exorcists
practicing in the United States today. He now works
out of his parish near Chicago.

1282
01:49:31,171 --> 01:49:37,838
Father Lucas Trevant has performed over
two thousand exorcisms. He continues to practice
in a township outside of Florence.

1283
01:53:38,251 --> 01:53:40,242
[English - US - SDH]

